Permits
Access to the British Indian Ocean Territory is restricted and a permit is required in advance of travel. There are no commercial flights
Coronavirus
The British Indian Ocean Territory Administration has introduced new measures in relation to coronavirus. See Coronavirus
Passport validity
Your passport must be valid for a minimum period of 6 months from the date of entry into British Indian Ocean Territory.
